,Recommended,249950,8633397,"Posted: 9 January, 2014",all,Hal,"Forge Quest is a voxel based Dungeon-exploring RPG game where you can explore towns, areas and delve into dungeons to find treasure, fight bosses and level up! As the game is currently in 'early access', the game is currently being updated but from what you get as of now, its a really great game and worth the price! The voxel aspect of the game is great and makes it feel cube-world-ish with a completely different approach. You can level up your character anyway you want, unlocking skills and abilities as you go through the game! The inventory and other menus are easy to navigate and it has an old style zelda appeal to it! As of writing this review, you cannot move or do anything once the attack animation has begun, which annoyed me a little, being able to move whilst attacking would make the game 100% better! All in all, a great game and since its still being developed, well worth it. - 8/10"
